de.axnsoftware.settings.impl.visitor

Class AbstractFieldVisitorImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.axnsoftware.settings.impl.visitor.AbstractFieldVisitorImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IVisitor<Field>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ArrayFieldVisitorImpl, ListFieldVisitorImpl, MapFieldVisitorImpl, PropertyClassFieldVisitorImpl, SimpleTypeFieldVisitorImpl

    public abstract class AbstractFieldVisitorImpl
extends Object
implements IVisitor<Field>
    The abstract class AbstractFieldVisitorImpl models the root of a hierarchy of derived implementation classes and it provides the default behaviour for all implementations of the IVisitor interface. It also encapsulated commonly used code to be reused by the concrete implementations.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Carsten Klein "cklein"
